<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Deerhunt statistics of {{ name|escape }} on #{{ channel_name|escape }}</title>

    <meta property="og:title"
          content="{{ name|escape }} statistics" />
    <meta property="og:type"
          content="profile" />
    <meta property="og:image"
          content="{{ avatar_url }}" />
    <meta property="og:description"
          content="{{ name|escape }} profile on #{{ channel_name|escape }}. {{ exp }} exp points!" />
    <meta property="og:site_name"
          content="DeerHunt" />

    <script
            src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.min.js"
            integrity="sha256-FgpCb/KJQlLNfOu91ta32o/NMZxltwRo8QtmkMRdAu8="
            crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="js/tipped/tipped.js"></script>

    <link rel="stylesheet"
          href="js/tipped/tipped.css" />


    <script src="https://code.highcharts.com/highcharts.js"></script>
    <script src="https://code.highcharts.com/modules/exporting.js"></script>
    <script src="https://code.highcharts.com/modules/export-data.js"></script>
    <style>
        .statistic {
            border-bottom-width: 1px;
            border-bottom-style: dotted;
            border-bottom-color: #666;
        }

        .graph {
            display: block;
            background: #E6E7ED;
            border-radius: 3px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .profile_picture {
            display: block;
            background: #E6E7ED;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 10px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 300px;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
        }

        html {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
            max-width: 100%;
        }

        .special-icons {
            text-align: center;
            background: #E6E7ED;
            border-radius: 3px;
            padding: 7px;
        }

        .special-icons img {
            height: 40px;
            width: 40px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 5px 10px;
            padding: 5px;

        }

        a:link, a:visited {
            color: #70ACE9;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        a:hover, a:active {
            color: #8AC7FF;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<img class="profile_picture"
     src="{{ avatar_url }}"
     alt="Profile Picture">

<h1>{{ name }} is hunting deer on <a href="deertats.php?cid={{ channel_id }}"> #{{ channel_name|escape }}</a></h1>


{% if true in badges %}
    <div class="special-icons">
        {% if badges['banned'] %}
            <img src="special-icons/banned.svg"
                 title="This player is banned on this server :(">
        {% endif %}

        {% if badges['no_weapon'] %}
            <img src="special-icons/no_weapon.svg"
                 title="This player had his weapon confiscated here :(">
        {% endif %}

        {% if badges['admin'] %}
            <img src="special-icons/admin.svg"
                 title="This user is a bot admin">
        {% endif %}

        {% if badges['moderator'] %}
            <img src="special-icons/moderator.svg"
                 title="This user is a bot moderator">
        {% endif %}

        {% if badges['translator'] %}
            <img src="special-icons/translator.svg"
                 title="This user helped translating the bot">
        {% endif %}

        {% if badges['bug_hunter'] %}
            <img src="special-icons/bug_hunter.svg"
                 title="This user is a bug hunter">
        {% endif %}

        {% if badges['proficient'] %}
            <img src="special-icons/proficient.svg"
                 title="This user is proficient with the bot and can help you on the support server">
        {% endif %}

        {% if badges['retired_staff'] %}
            <img src="special-icons/retired_staff.svg"
                 title="This user retired from the bot staff">
        {% endif %}

        {% if badges['partner'] %}
            <img src="special-icons/partner.svg"
                 title="This user is a bot partner">
        {% endif %}

        {% if badges['donator'] %}
            <img src="special-icons/donator.svg"
                 title="This user donated to the bot">
        {% endif %}

        {% if badges['enigma_event_winner_june_2018'] %}
            <img src="special-icons/enigma_event_winner_june_2018.svg"
                 title="This user won the DeerEnigma event of june 2018">
        {% endif %}

    </div>
{% endif %}


<h2>General statistics</h2>

<p>
    With <span class="statistic">{{ givebacks }}</span> days played, and <span class="statistic">{{ exp }}</span>
    experience points, you can be sure that <span class="statistic">{{ name|escape }}</span> is a good <em>Deer</em>
    Hunter
</p>
<p>
    In fact, they have some good reflexes too, with a best time before a deer was killed that seems to be
    <span class="statistic">{{ best_time | number_format(2, '.', ',') }}</span> seconds
</p>


{% if true in achievements %}
    <h2>Achievements</h2>
    <div class="special-icons">

        {% if achievements['time_played_1'] %}
            <img src="achievements-icons/time_played_1.svg"
                 title="This hunter played for more than a week">
        {% endif %}

        {% if achievements['time_played_2'] %}
            <img src="achievements-icons/time_played_2.svg"
                 title="This player played for more than a month">
        {% endif %}

        {% if achievements['clueless'] %}
            <img src="achievements-icons/clueless.svg"
                 title="This player probably don't understand that they should earn experience">
        {% endif %}

        {% if achievements['scientist'] %}
            <img src="achievements-icons/scientist.svg"
                 title="This player is halfway to the top">
        {% endif %}

        {% if achievements['max_level'] %}
            <img src="achievements-icons/max_level.svg"
                 title="This player reached the maximum level in the game">
        {% endif %}

        {% if achievements['cheater'] %}
            <img src="achievements-icons/cheater.svg"
                 title="This player probably cheated to reach that amount of exp">
        {% endif %}

        {% if achievements['baby_lover'] %}
            <img src="achievements-icons/baby_lover.svg"
                 title="This player killed less than 5 baby deer">
        {% endif %}


        {% if achievements['murderer'] %}
            <img src="achievements-icons/murderer.svg"
                 title="This player murdered someone">
        {% endif %}


        {% if achievements['first_blood'] %}
            <img src="achievements-icons/first_blood.svg"
                 title="This player killed his first deer">
        {% endif %}

        {% if achievements['deer_killed_1'] %}
            <img src="achievements-icons/deer_killed_1.svg"
                 title="More than 10 deer killed">
        {% endif %}

        {% if achievements['deer_killed_2'] %}
            <img src="achievements-icons/deer_killed_2.svg"
                 title="More than 100 deer killed">
        {% endif %}

        {% if achievements['deer_killed_3'] %}
            <img src="achievements-icons/deer_killed_3.svg"
                 title="More than 500 deer killed">
        {% endif %}

        {% if achievements['deer_killed_4'] %}
            <img src="achievements-icons/deer_killed_4.svg"
                 title="More than 1000 deer killed">
        {% endif %}

        {% if achievements['deer_killed_5'] %}
            <img src="achievements-icons/deer_killed_5.svg"
                 title="More than 2000 deer killed">
        {% endif %}

        {% if achievements['deer_killed_6'] %}
            <img src="achievements-icons/deer_killed_6.svg"
                 title="More than 4000 deer killed">
        {% endif %}


        {% if achievements['lucky_user'] %}
            <img src="achievements-icons/lucky_user.svg"
                 title="More than 500 exp won with a clover">
        {% endif %}


    </div>

    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(document).ready(function () {
            Tipped.create('.simple-tooltip');
        });
    </script>
{% endif %}


<h2>Deer killed</h2>

<div id="deer_killed"
     class="graph"></div>


<script>

    Highcharts.chart('deer_killed', {
        chart: {
            type: 'column'
        },
        credits: {
            enabled: false
        },
        title: {
            text: 'Types of deer killed by {{ name|escape('js') }}'
        },
        subtitle: {
            text: 'Generated {{ "now"|date }}'
        },
        xAxis: {
            type: 'category',
            labels: {
                rotation: -45,
                style: {
                    fontSize: '13px',
                    fontFamily: 'Verdana, sans-serif'
                }
            }
        },
        yAxis: {
            min: 0,
            title: {
                text: 'Number of deer killed'
            }
        },
        legend: {
            enabled: false
        },
        tooltip: {
            pointFormat: '{point.y} killed'
        },
        series: [{
            name: 'Deer',
            data: [
                ['Normal Deer', {{ killed_normal_deer }}],
                ['Super Deer', {{ killed_super_deer }}],
                ['Baby Deer', {{ killed_baby_deer }}],
                ['MOAD', {{ killed_mother_of_all_deer }}],
                ['Mechanical Deer', {{ killed_mechanical_deer }}],
                ['Players (oops)', {{ killed_players }}]
            ],

            dataLabels: {
                enabled: true,
                //rotation: -90,
                color: '#FFFFFF',
                align: 'center',
                format: '{point.y}', // one decimal
                y: -10 // 10 pixels down from the top
            }
        }]
    });


</script>


<h2>Objects in backpack</h2>

<p>
    In <span class="statistic">{{ name|escape }}</span>'s backpack, I can see
    <span class="statistic">{{ chargeurs }}</span> chargers and <span class="statistic">{{ balles }}</span> bullets
    loaded in their weapon (and the last weapon giveback they used was
    on {% if lastGiveback|date('Y-m-d') == "now"|date('Y-m-d') %}today, {% endif %}the
    <span class="statistic">{{ lastGiveback|date("m/d/Y") }}</span>)

</p>
<ul>
    {#How to compare dates :)#}
    {% if sight > 0 %}
        <li>
            They have a <strong>sight</strong> mounted on their weapon good for
            <span class="statistic">{{ sight }}</span> more shots.
        </li>
    {% endif %}
    {% if ap_ammo > "now"|date('U') %}
        <li>
            They have some <strong>Armor Piercing ammo</strong> until
            <span class="statistic">{{ ap_ammo|date("m/d/Y \\a\\t g:ia") }}</span>
        </li>
    {% endif %}
    {% if detecteurInfra > "now"|date('U')  and detecteur_infra_shots_left >= 0 %}
        <li>
            They have an <strong>infrared detector</strong> on their weapon until
            <span class="statistic">{{ detecteurInfra|date("m/d/Y \\a\\t g:ia") }}</span>, that can prevent
            <span class="statistic">{{ detecteur_infra_shots_left }}</span> shots
        </li>
    {% endif %}
    {% if explosive_ammo > "now"|date('U') %}
        <li>
            They have some <strong>explosive ammo</strong> until
            <span class="statistic">{{ explosive_ammo|date("m/d/Y \\a\\t g:ia") }}</span>
        </li>
    {% endif %}
    {% if graisse > "now"|date('U') %}
        <li>
            They have some <strong>grease</strong> in their weapon that will dry and wear out on
            <span class="statistic">{{ graisse|date("m/d/Y \\a\\t g:ia") }}</span>
        </li>
    {% endif %}
    {% if life_insurance > "now"|date('U') %}
        <li>
            They have a valid <strong>life insurance</strong> policy that will least until
            <span class="statistic">{{ life_insurance|date("m/d/Y \\a\\t g:ia") }}</span>
        </li>
    {% endif %}
    {% if silencieux > "now"|date('U') %}
        <li>
            They have a <strong>silencer</strong> mounted on their weapon that will break on
            <span class="statistic">{{ silencieux|date("m/d/Y \\a\\t g:ia") }}</span>
        </li>
    {% endif %}
    {% if sunglasses > "now"|date('U') %}
        <li>
            Swag incoming, they have some <strong>sunglasses</strong> right in the face the rented until
            <span class="statistic">{{ sunglasses|date("m/d/Y \\a\\t g:ia") }}</span>
        </li>
    {% endif %}
    {% if trefle > "now"|date('U') %}
        <li>
            The luck is with them, because they have a <strong>4-leaf clover</strong> that gives them
            <span class="statistic">{{ trefle_exp }}</span> more experience points by deer killed until
            <span class="statistic">{{ trefle|date("m/d/Y \\a\\t g:ia") }}</span>
        </li>
    {% endif %}
</ul>

<h2>Shots statistics</h2>
<p>
    <span class="statistic">{{ name|escape }}</span> fired a whopping total of
    <span class="statistic">{{ shoots_fired }}</span> shots. Hopefully, a lot of them killed a deer!
</p>

<div id="shots_fired"
     class="graph"></div>
<script>
    function compare_data_arrays(a, b) {
        // Reverse the order
        return b.y - a.y;
    }

    Highcharts.chart('shots_fired', {
        chart: {
            plotBackgroundColor: null,
            plotBorderWidth: null,
            plotShadow: false,
            type: 'pie'
        },
        title: {
            text: 'Repartiton of shots fired by {{ name|escape('js') }}'
        },
        tooltip: {
            pointFormat: '{series.name}: <b>{point.percentage:.1f}% ({point.y})</b>'
        },
        subtitle: {
            text: 'Generated {{ "now"|date }}'
        },
        plotOptions: {
            pie: {
                allowPointSelect: true,
                cursor: 'pointer',
                dataLabels: {
                    enabled: true,
                    format: '<b>{point.name}</b>: {point.percentage:.1f}% ({point.y})',
                    style: {
                        color: (Highcharts.theme && Highcharts.theme.contrastTextColor) || 'black'
                    }
                }
            }
        },
        series: [{
            name: 'Shots',
            colorByPoint: true,
            data: [{
                name: 'Shots killing a deer',
                y: {{ killed_deer }},
                sliced: true,
                selected: true
            }, {
                name: 'Shots harming a deer',
                y: {{ shoots_harmed_deer }},
                sliced: true
            }, {
                name: 'Shots missed',
                y: {{ shoots_missed }}
            }, {
                name: 'Shots where {{ name|escape('js') }} injured himself',
                y: {{ self_killing_shoots }}
            }, {
                name: 'Shots tried with no weapon',
                y: {{ shoots_without_weapon }}
            }, {
                name: 'Shots tried without bullets',
                y: {{ shoots_without_bullets }}
            }, {
                name: 'Shots tried with a jammed weapon',
                y: {{ shoots_with_jammed_weapon }}
            }, {
                name: 'Shots tried while wet',
                y: {{ shoots_tried_while_wet }}
            }, {
                name: 'Shots with a sabotaged weapon',
                y: {{ shoots_sabotaged }}
            }, {
                name: 'Shots where no deer were on the channel',
                y: {{ shoots_no_deer }}
            }, {
                name: 'Shots jamming the weapon',
                y: {{ shoots_jamming_weapon }}
            }, {
                name: 'Shots stopped by an infrared detector',
                y: {{ shoots_infrared_detector }}
            }, {
                name: 'Shots frightening a deer',
                y: {{ shoots_frightened }}
            }, {
                name: 'Shots almost killing a deer',
                y: {{ shoots_almost_killed }}
            }].sort(compare_data_arrays)
        }]
    });
</script>

<h2>Misc statistics</h2>

<p>
    <span class="statistic">{{ name|escape }}</span> won a total of
    <span class="statistic">{{ exp_won_with_clover }}</span> experience points by using a clover (that's
    <span class="statistic">{{ (exp_won_with_clover/killed_deer)|number_format(2, '.', ',') }}</span>
                                                     experience points by deer killed). They also earned
    <span class="statistic">{{ life_insurence_rewards }}</span> exp using a life insurance.
</p>

<p>
    They found <span class="statistic">{{ trashFound }}</span> trash items in the bushes,
    <span class="statistic">{{ found_explosive_ammo }}</span> explosive ammo boxes,
    <span class="statistic">{{ found_almost_empty_explosive_ammo }}</span> almost empty boxes of explosive ammo,
    <span class="statistic">{{ found_chargers }}</span> magazines (and
    <span class="statistic">{{ found_chargers_not_taken }}</span> they couldn't take because their backpack was full), and
    <span class="statistic">{{ found_bullets }}</span> bullets (plus
    <span class="statistic">{{ found_bullets_not_taken }}</span> they couldn't take because, well, weapon fully loaded)

    Also, they found deer-grease <span class="statistic">{{ found_grease }}</span> times,
    found <span class="statistic">{{ found_silencers }}</span> silencers
    and <span class="statistic">{{ found_infrared_detectors }}</span> infrared detectors

</p>

<p>
    <span class="statistic">{{ name|escape }}</span> murdered <span class="statistic">{{ murders }}</span> fellow hunters.
</p>

<p>
    <span class="statistic">{{ name|escape }}</span>
    is {% if unneeded_reloads < 5 %}not really{% endif %}{% if unneeded_reloads > 50 %}really{% endif %} reload hungry and tried to reload
    <span class="statistic">{{ unneeded_reloads }}</span> times with a full clip!
</p>




<script type="text/javascript">
    $(document).ready(function() {
        Tipped.create('.special-icons img');
    });
</script>

</body>
</html>
